{"_path":"/maps/_person/aristotle","_dir":"_person","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"亚里士多德（BC384~BC322）","description":"古希腊哲学家，亚历山大大帝的老师，西方哲学的集大成者。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"亚里士多德的生平"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亚里士多德的生平?"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亚里士多德是柏拉图的学生，亚历山大的老师。他是一位百科全书式的科学家，堪称希腊哲学的集大成者。其写作涉及伦理学、形而上学、心理学、经济学、神学、政治学、修辞学、自然科学、教育学、诗歌、风俗，以及雅典法律。他的著作构建了西方哲学的第一个广泛系统，包含道德、美学、逻辑和科学、政治和玄学。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"古希腊哲学家中最博学的人物。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"name","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"马克思"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"古代的黑格尔。\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"name","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"恩格斯"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"亚里士多德关于精神大脑和心的认识"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亚里士多德关于精神、大脑和心的认识？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与希波克拉底相反，亚里士多德认为"},{"type":"element","tag":"u","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"神智在心"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。亚里士多德（及多位大思想家）认为，大脑是不太重要的器官，灵魂位于心脏。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"references"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"References"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E4%BA%9A%E9%87%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%A4%9A%E5%BE%B7/26769","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"亚里士多德"}]}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"references","depth":2,"text":"References"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_person:aristotle.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_person/a